ion":"soulsilver","text":"It can swim at speeds of 75 mph by jetting seawater through its body. It is the bandit of the sea."},{"version":"black","text":"Its fangs rip through sheet iron. It swims at 75 mph and is known as \u201cThe Bully of the Sea.\u201d"},{"version":"white","text":"Its fangs rip through sheet iron. It swims at 75 mph and is known as \u201cThe Bully of the Sea.\u201d"},{"version":"black-2","text":"Its fangs rip through sheet iron. It swims at 75 mph and is known as \u201cThe Bully of the Sea.\u201d"},{"version":"white-2","text":"Its fangs rip through sheet iron. It swims at 75 mph and is known as \u201cThe Bully of the Sea.\u201d"},{"version":"x","text":"Its fangs rip through sheet iron. It swims at 75 mph and is known as \u201cThe Bully of the Sea.\u201d"},{"version":"y","text":"It can swim at speeds of 75 mph by jetting seawater through its body. It is the bandit of the sea."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Nicknamed \u201cthe bully of the sea,\u201d Sharpedo is widely feared. Its cruel fangs grow back immediately if they snap off. Just one of these Pok\u00e9mon can thoroughly tear apart a supertanker."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Sharpedo can swim at speeds of up to 75 mph by jetting seawater out of its backside. This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s drawback is its inability to swim long distances."},{"version":"sun","text":"It pursues its prey at speeds of 75 mph and finishes them off with fangs that can crush iron. It is known as the bully of the sea."},{"version":"moon","text":"It has a sad history. In the past, its dorsal fin was a treasured foodstuff, so this Pok\u00e9mon became a victim of overfishing."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"People believe that carrying one of its discarded fangs will prevent mishaps at sea, so the fangs are made into accessories."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It drinks in seawater and jets it from its rear to propel itself. It\u2019s very sensitive to the scent of blood."},{"version":"sword","text":"As soon a